.put(input);\n        source.flip();\n\n        ByteBuffer compressed = ByteBuffer.allocateDirect(compressor.maxCompressedLength(input.length));\n        int compressedSize = compressor.compress(\n                MemorySegment.ofBuffer(source),\n                MemorySegment.ofBuffer(compressed));\n        assertThat(compressedSize).isPositive();\n\n        compressed.limit(compressedSize);\n        ByteBuffer restored = ByteBuffer.allocateDirect(input.length);\n        int restoredSize = decompressor.decompress(\n                MemorySegment.ofBuffer(compressed),\n                MemorySegment.ofBuffer(restored));\n\n        ByteBuffer restoredView = restored.duplicate();\n        restoredView.limit(restoredSize);\n        byte[] actual = new byte[restoredView.remaining()];\n        restoredView.get(actual);\n        assertThat(actual).isEqualTo(input);\n    }\n\n    private static byte[] repeatedPayload() {\n        String sentence = \"Aircompressor LZ4 direct-buffer round trip exercises unsafe address access.\\n\";\n        StringBuilder builder = new StringBuilder(sentence.length() * 64);\n        for (int i = 0; i < 64; i++) {\n            builder.append(sentence).append(i).append('\\n');\n        }\n        return builder.toString().getBytes(StandardCharsets.UTF_8);\n    }\n}\n"}], "isError": false, "timestamp": 1780817183278}]}
